Dialogue: 0.0:00:36.45.0:00:38.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..There he is! Cut him off!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:38.95.0:00:41.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Stop in the name of...
Dialogue: 0.0:00:41.16.0:00:42.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Right there!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:47.87.0:00:49.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Go!  - Go!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:53.00.0:00:54.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He's over there! Get him!
Dialogue: 0.0:00:58.70.0:01:01.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- There he is.  - Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:07.33.0:01:08.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..After him!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.08.0:01:14.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:33.29.0:01:34.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..An Earthbender.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:37.50.0:01:38.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Hurry!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:03.04.0:02:04.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:04.25.0:02:05.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Now! Now!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:07.54.0:02:08.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He went that way!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:12.62.0:02:14.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Get that to the Earth King.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:14.95.0:02:16.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..They're going to start a war!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:16.66.0:02:18.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- There!  - Go now!
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.87.0:03:01.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're too late.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:01.70.0:03:04.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Your battle plans are already on their way to the Earth Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:04.75.0:03:05.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Good.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:06.83.0:03:09.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..That means all eyes will be on the Earth Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:11.54.0:03:13.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..All eyes but ours.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:16.29.0:03:18.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We'll be prepared for your attack.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:19.08.0:03:21.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..When your king receives those plans.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:22.41.0:03:25.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..he will redirect his forces to your borders
Dialogue: 0.0:03:26.41.0:03:29.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and rally the support of the other nations.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:29.50.0:03:33.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The Water Tribes and the Air Nomads and the entire world
Dialogue: 0.0:03:34.00.0:03:37.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..will turn their attention to the Earthbenders.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:43.62.0:03:45.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You... you wanted us to know?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:49.25.0:03:50.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We aren't the real target.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:54.50.0:03:56.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..My sights are set higher.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:58.00.0:03:59.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Much higher.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:00.04.0:04:00.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Why?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:02.91.0:04:04.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:11.37.0:04:13.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Because it is our time.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:25.95.0:04:27.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..A masterful ruse. Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.45.0:04:31.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But tactically. the Airbenders are not the threat.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:33.16.0:04:35.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..This isn't about the Airbenders.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:35.79.0:04:37.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..This is about one who lives among them.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:37.66.0:04:41.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The only one who could possibly stand in our way.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:41.00.0:04:43.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But the Avatar is yet to be revealed.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:45.37.0:04:48.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Which is why we have to kill them all.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:57.04.0:04:58.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Kyoshi:{\b0}{\c} {\c&H38d832&\i1}Water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:00.33.0:05:01.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:04.08.0:05:05.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:07.70.0:05:08.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:12.33.0:05:16.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}For millennia. the four nations have lived in harmony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:17.25.0:05:19.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}a peace made possible by the Avatar...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:23.62.0:05:27.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}the one person with the ability to master all four elements{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:27.79.0:05:31.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}and protect the delicate balance between nations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:35.20.0:05:36.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}When one Avatar dies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:37.41.0:05:41.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}their spirit is reborn into a new body in an eternal cycle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:43.04.0:05:45.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Since the death of the last Avatar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:45.37.0:05:48.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}the new incarnation has yet to emerge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:48.70.0:05:53.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}And so Fire Lord Sozin. the ruthless leader of the Fire Nation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:53.08.0:05:57.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}believes this is his moment to launch a merciless campaign{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:57.12.0:05:58.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}to conquer the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:05:59.16.0:06:02.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}His first step is to eliminate the one person{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:06:02.12.0:06:04.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}who could stand in his way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:06:04.41.0:06:07.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}The next master of all four elements.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:06:07.00.0:06:11.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}an Airbender who may not be ready for the responsibility of becoming{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:06:12.33.0:06:13.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}the Avatar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:06:18.86.0:06:26.02.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\an7\c&H9bbdd0&}Subtitle by {\c&H44529c&\b1}Sailor420{\b0}
Dialogue: 0.0:06:18.86.0:06:26.02.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\an3\c&H9bbdd0&}Hope you enjoy the show
Dialogue: 0.0:06:58.12.0:06:59.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:02.33.0:07:03.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:10.41.0:07:11.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Hey. look!  - {\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} Yeah!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:16.12.0:07:17.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Wow!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:21.58.0:07:22.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Who else?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:29.79.0:07:30.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Whoa!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:38.04.0:07:39.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Show-off.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:39.70.0:07:42.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- What? I was just enjoying the view.  - Ha.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:43.54.0:07:45.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Monk Tsutop was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:45.45.0:07:47.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You skipped training again!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:47.54.0:07:51.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's all the same drills. You know I already know all this stuff.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:51.41.0:07:52.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:53.87.0:07:58.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You may be more advanced than the others. but there's much you have to learn.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:59.12.0:08:00.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:01.54.0:08:06.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..there may come a day when you wish you'd spent more time with your teachers.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:11.75.0:08:15.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Now. you and the other students better go help set up
Dialogue: 0.0:08:15.04.0:08:16.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..for the Great Comet Festival.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:17.79.0:08:19.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Still a lot of work to be done
Dialogue: 0.0:08:19.04.0:08:22.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..before the Air Nomads from the other temples arrive.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:22.29.0:08:23.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..How many are coming?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:23.62.0:08:26.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Wait. What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:27.04.0:08:28.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Look! Up there!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:30.41.0:08:31.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Look at all of them.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:34.12.0:08:35.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Wow! There's so many!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:36.33.0:08:37.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Look at all of them!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:37.91.0:08:39.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..All of them.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:41.58.0:08:43.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on. Aang! They're right up there!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:45.08.0:08:46.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} Wait up!
Dialogue: 0.0:08:49.04.0:08:50.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Did you tell him?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:53.00.0:08:55.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- It wasn't the right time.  - The right time?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:55.79.0:08:57.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We don't have the luxury of waiting for the right time.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:58.62.0:09:01.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We need to go talk to the council now.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.41.0:09:10.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Aang has always been a prodigy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:09:10.58.0:09:13.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The youngest Airbender in history
Dialogue: 0.0:09:13.16.0:09:15.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..to receive the markings of a master.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.20.0:09:18.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But he is only 12.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.91.0:09:21.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We can't ask this of him.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:21.08.0:09:23.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Fire Lord Sozin is planning to attack the Earth Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:23.58.0:09:26.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The Water Tribes are already sending the warriors to aid the Earthbenders.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:26.70.0:09:28.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and we need to help them as well.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:28.54.0:09:30.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And we need the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:30.16.0:09:35.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Yes. Aang is powerful. but there's much he still needs to learn
Dialogue: 0.0:09:35.83.0:09:37.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..about responsibility.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:37.54.0:09:39.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..expectations.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:39.50.0:09:40.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:41.91.0:09:45.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Most of all. he needs to know who he is.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:47.04.0:09:49.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..If we send him away before he learns these things.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:50.08.0:09:53.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..he could fail to be everything we need him to be.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:55.00.0:09:57.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And he and the world
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.20.0:10:00.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..might never recover from that.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:00.83.0:10:04.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The role of the Avatar is a heavy responsibility.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:04.83.0:10:06.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..not meant for a child.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.08.0:10:10.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But it is not our place to choose who bears that burden.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:10.04.0:10:14.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and I fear you've grown too close to Aang to see that. Brother Gyatso.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:14.70.0:10:15.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang must leave immediately
Dialogue: 0.0:10:15.95.0:10:18.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..to begin training in the other bending disciplines.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:18.95.0:10:19.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and we can only hope
Dialogue: 0.0:10:19.83.0:10:22.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..that it is not too late for him to make a difference.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.25.0:10:33.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Are comet festivals always this much work?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.29.0:10:35.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Well. the last one was a hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:35.00.0:10:36.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:36.08.0:10:38.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm actually not old enough to have seen that.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:38.83.0:10:42.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Could have fooled me.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:46.25.0:10:48.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Remember the last time I brought you here?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:48.66.0:10:50.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sure. When I got my tattoos.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:50.45.0:10:52.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Most receive their markings in the main hall.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:52.58.0:10:57.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but I wanted you to receive yours in the presence of Yangchen.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:57.00.0:10:59.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..the last Air Nomad to be the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.83.0:11:02.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..When she died. the next Avatar was born
Dialogue: 0.0:11:02.54.0:11:05.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..into the following nation in the eternal cycle.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:05.12.0:11:07.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..so after Yangchen's death
Dialogue: 0.0:11:08.45.0:11:13.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..came Kuruk of the Water Tribes. then Kyoshi of the Earth Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0.0:11:13.16.0:11:14.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And then Roku in the Fire Nation.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:14.87.0:11:17.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Which means the next Avatar
Dialogue: 0.0:11:18.54.0:11:20.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..will once again be an Airbender.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.91.0:11:25.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Her spirit echoes in one of us.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:27.20.0:11:30.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang. you have always been special.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:30.95.0:11:33.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The most talented Airbender I have ever known.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:34.12.0:11:36.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I never asked to be special.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:36.00.0:11:37.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But you are.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:38.54.0:11:39.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:40.45.0:11:43.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..you are the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:47.00.0:11:50.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Gyatso:{\b0}{\c} The Fire Nation has embarked on a dark path.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:50.20.0:11:53.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Their actions threaten to throw the world out of balance.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:53.25.0:11:58.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Only the Avatar. the one person who can master all four elements.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:58.37.0:11:59.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..can save the world.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:00.75.0:12:02.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The world needs the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:03.50.0:12:05.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The world needs you. Aang.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.41.0:12:09.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're to leave right away so you can begin training in the other disciplines.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:10.87.0:12:12.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Right away?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:12.20.0:12:15.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Leave my friends? Leave home? Leave you?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:15.45.0:12:16.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Now. this
Dialogue: 0.0:12:17.62.0:12:19.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..would be a huge burden for anyone.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:21.20.0:12:23.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but you're not just anyone. Aang.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:23.66.0:12:25.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're strong
Dialogue: 0.0:12:26.00.0:12:27.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and kind
Dialogue: 0.0:12:27.87.0:12:29.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and generous.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:30.16.0:12:31.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Remember that.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:31.58.0:12:34.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Always remember who you are
Dialogue: 0.0:12:34.70.0:12:38.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..because I can't imagine a better person to have been given this power.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:39.45.0:12:42.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't want... the power.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:43.29.0:12:47.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Which is why you will make a great Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:50.00.0:12:51.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Why do I have to be different?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:53.16.0:12:54.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Can't I just
Dialogue: 0.0:12:55.33.0:12:57.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..keep pretending that I'm your friend?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:00.37.0:13:01.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You are my friend.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:03.25.0:13:07.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You... will always be my friend.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.33.0:13:46.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} Hey. Appa.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:48.54.0:13:50.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Couldn't sleep either. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:55.37.0:13:57.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Gyatso says I'm supposed to be the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:58.70.0:14:00.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Me.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:00.91.0:14:03.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Monks don't even trust me to feed the baby bison.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:03.08.0:14:05.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and I'm supposed to save the world?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:07.91.0:14:11.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He said I need to remember who I am.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:12.04.0:14:13.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But I know who I am.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:14.54.0:14:16.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I like to play airball and eat banana cakes
Dialogue: 0.0:14:16.83.0:14:19.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and goof off with my friends.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:19.00.0:14:20.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..That's who I am.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:21.08.0:14:23.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..not someone who can stop the Fire Nation.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.75.0:14:25.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Not someone who can stop a war.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:30.70.0:14:34.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The other kids always say I'm lucky because of the things I could do.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:34.20.0:14:36.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but I'd trade places with any of them.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:38.08.0:14:39.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't wanna leave.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:39.75.0:14:41.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't want the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:41.95.0:14:45.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm scared of my power. I'm scared of being alone!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:55.29.0:14:56.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:06.12.0:15:07.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're right.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:07.66.0:15:10.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I just need to go up where things always make more sense.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:12.25.0:15:13.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..At least for now.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:14.20.0:15:16.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Yip. yip!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:38.70.0:15:39.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Remember.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:40.62.0:15:42.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..no survivors.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:05.75.0:16:08.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Brothers and sisters. we're under attack!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:18.79.0:16:20.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Yah!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:48.79.0:16:51.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- What's going on?  - Come with me. quickly!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:52.62.0:16:53.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Where's Aang?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:54.83.0:16:57.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:48.12.0:17:51.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Gyatso:{\b0}{\c} Quickly. move along.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.08.0:18:01.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} It's getting kind of rough. Appa. Maybe we should head back home?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.12.0:18:15.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Gyatso:{\b0}{\c} That's it. Stay quiet. You'll be safe in there.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.16.0:18:16.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Right into the corner.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:17.62.0:18:19.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Stay down.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:56.58.0:18:57.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's okay. Appa!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:57.79.0:18:59.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} Steady!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:19.75.0:20:22.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Oh!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:43.08.0:20:45.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You may have prevailed on another night.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.75.0:20:53.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But not when we have the power of the comet!
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.16.0:21:01.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Ah!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:13.50.0:22:15.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on!
Dialogue: 0.0:22:23.87.0:22:25.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..All right. listen up.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:25.75.0:22:27.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We've been manning the wall in three-hour shifts.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:27.95.0:22:32.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but it seems some of you can't be trusted to stay at your posts.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:32.62.0:22:33.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..So from now on.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:34.58.0:22:37.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..two people at all times. meaning twice as many shifts.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:39.20.0:22:40.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:40.83.0:22:43.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Didn't think so. Okay. back to your duties.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:43.12.0:22:45.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on. let's go.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:46.20.0:22:47.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:48.41.0:22:50.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The fishing boats came back empty.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:50.16.0:22:52.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Just proves if you want something done right. gotta do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:53.29.0:22:55.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..They don't appreciate your incredible leadership skills.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:55.54.0:22:57.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..That's right. They don't realize it.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:58.33.0:22:59.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Very funny.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:02.79.0:23:03.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Katara!
Dialogue: 0.0:23:11.16.0:23:12.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..So where were you before?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:15.16.0:23:17.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You were waterbending again. weren't you?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:18.37.0:23:20.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Don't worry. No one could see me.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:21.41.0:23:22.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Not that it matters.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:23.37.0:23:26.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Of course it matters. If the Fire Nation finds out you're a Waterbender--
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.25.0:23:29.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..No one from the Fire Nation has approached the village in years.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:30.04.0:23:32.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Besides. there's nothing to see.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:33.45.0:23:35.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..An otter penguin could bend more water than I could.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:37.37.0:23:38.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's probably for the best.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:38.70.0:23:41.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You should be helping out more around the village anyway.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:42.50.0:23:44.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Not everything is about preparing to fight.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:45.41.0:23:48.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- We're at war.  - Waterbending is what built our culture.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:48.54.0:23:50.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Our way of life. Keeping it alive is our duty.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:50.70.0:23:53.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Keeping ourselves alive is our duty.  - I know that.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:54.29.0:23:57.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- And if Dad were here--  - But he's not here! I am!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:05.79.0:24:06.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Katara.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:09.62.0:24:12.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Katara. Sulk later. paddle now.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:21.75.0:24:22.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Good job.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:22.66.0:24:24.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm not doing this.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:42.79.0:24:44.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka!
Dialogue: 0.0:24:51.95.0:24:53.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:55.16.0:24:57.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Oh no. No. no. that's not good.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:03.20.0:25:04.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..What is that?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:09.12.0:25:10.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Sokka:{\b0}{\c} Huh. weird.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:18.75.0:25:21.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We need to get that canoe. or we're gonna end up as fish food.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:22.37.0:25:23.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..which would be ironic.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:52.83.0:25:54.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Maybe I could float over on some ice?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:12.25.0:26:14.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Uh. Katara?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:51.08.0:26:52.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Finally.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:24.45.0:27:25.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Where did he come from?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:26.54.0:27:27.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:29.20.0:27:31.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Oh! Nice. Nice. We're not gonna die.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:33.62.0:27:34.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:35.91.0:27:38.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Whoa! Whoa! Whoa! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:39.37.0:27:41.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're not thinking of leaving him?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:41.04.0:27:44.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Katara. a strange. glowy iceberg just exploded and left behind
Dialogue: 0.0:27:44.83.0:27:46.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..a mysterious little bald person.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:46.58.0:27:50.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..What part of that makes you think. "Great. let's bring him home"?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:50.12.0:27:52.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka. he's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:53.33.0:27:55.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We can't just leave him out here.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:55.79.0:27:57.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't like this. but why listen to me?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:57.91.0:28:00.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm just responsible for the safety of the village.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:18.87.0:28:21.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- He looks dead.  - What's that mark on his head?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:23.20.0:28:24.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:29.54.0:28:32.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It can't be.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:32.04.0:28:33.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..What is it. Gran Gran?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:33.91.0:28:36.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..This is an Airbender.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:36.54.0:28:39.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's impossible. Airbenders don't exist anymore.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:40.70.0:28:43.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Well. we won't get any answers until he wakes up.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:43.75.0:28:44.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We need to let him rest.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:46.50.0:28:47.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:58.62.0:29:00.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The only settlement in that area is Water Tribe Village
Dialogue: 0.0:29:00.70.0:29:03.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..in the South Pole territory. That's where we have to go.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:03.00.0:29:05.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Where you think we'll find the Avatar?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:05.62.0:29:06.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Because of the light?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:07.70.0:29:09.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You think I'm imagining things?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:10.95.0:29:15.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sometimes. light beams are nothing more than celestial glimmers in the winter sky.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:15.62.0:29:19.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..For three years. I've chased down every hint. every rumor.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:19.62.0:29:22.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..every whisper of the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:22.66.0:29:26.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and I'll keep doing it for another three years if I have to.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:26.16.0:29:29.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Prince Zuko. I don't think your father would want you--
Dialogue: 0.0:29:29.04.0:29:33.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..My father has banished me until I find the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:33.00.0:29:35.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and that's exactly what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:36.16.0:29:39.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..All I'm saying is. it's hard to see you get your hopes up
Dialogue: 0.0:29:39.70.0:29:41.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..every time you see a...
Dialogue: 0.0:29:42.08.0:29:43.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..a sign.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:48.70.0:29:50.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It'll all be worth it once I return home in glory
Dialogue: 0.0:29:50.70.0:29:53.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..to take my place as the rightful heir to the Fire Lord.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:56.75.0:30:00.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Perhaps it's time to consider that the throne isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:04.16.0:30:05.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It may not have been for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:10.12.0:30:11.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But for me...
Dialogue: 0.0:30:14.50.0:30:15.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..it's my destiny.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:40.95.0:30:42.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:53.20.0:30:54.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:14.04.0:31:15.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Got you!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:15.58.0:31:16.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:18.25.0:31:20.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Hey. get away from him!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:20.58.0:31:22.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..What are you thinking? Have you forgotten your training?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:22.79.0:31:25.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..What'd I say about keeping your guard up? He could be the enemy.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:25.33.0:31:26.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The enemy?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:27.25.0:31:28.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm not the enemy.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:28.91.0:31:30.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Then who are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:30.95.0:31:31.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm Aang.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:34.33.0:31:35.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Where am I?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:35.95.0:31:37.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- How'd I get here?  - You tell me.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:37.83.0:31:38.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Wait.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:39.66.0:31:40.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Appa?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:41.54.0:31:42.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Appa!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:43.25.0:31:44.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Where's Appa?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:45.79.0:31:46.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:47.62.0:31:48.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:49.25.0:31:50.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:51.00.0:31:52.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..That's not strange at all.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:53.62.0:31:56.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- This is unbelievable.  - Appa!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:56.04.0:31:57.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He is an Airbender.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:08.83.0:32:10.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Have you seen Appa?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:10.50.0:32:12.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..My sky bison.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:13.00.0:32:16.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Six legs. horns. brown arrows?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:17.45.0:32:18.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sky bison.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:19.25.0:32:22.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Sky bison!  - Repeating it doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:25.70.0:32:28.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Whoa!  - What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:30.00.0:32:31.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Appa!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:41.50.0:32:42.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sky bison.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:46.29.0:32:47.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You say you went down in the storm?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:47.95.0:32:49.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It came upon us suddenly.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:49.79.0:32:52.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The weather went crazy just after I left home.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:52.58.0:32:54.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The Southern Air Temple.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:55.66.0:32:57.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Where the Air Nomads live.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.04.0:33:00.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Well. not all the Air Nomads.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:00.12.0:33:03.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but most of them had just arrived for the Great Comet Festival.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:03.08.0:33:04.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The Great Comet Festival.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:07.75.0:33:08.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Gran Gran?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:11.12.0:33:15.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Water. earth. fire. air.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:15.33.0:33:19.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Long ago. the four nations lived together in harmony.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:19.37.0:33:23.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Then everything changed when the Fire Nation attacked.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:24.12.0:33:27.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Only the Avatar. master of all four elements.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:27.95.0:33:29.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..could stop them.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:30.08.0:33:33.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But when the world needed him most.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:33.70.0:33:34.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..he vanished.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:36.12.0:33:39.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And so the Fire Nation marched and laid waste.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:39.62.0:33:42.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..plunging us into a time of darkness.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:43.37.0:33:45.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Everyone in the village knows this story.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:46.79.0:33:49.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but you don't. do you. young man?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:50.33.0:33:56.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Just as you don't know that Airbenders haven't been seen in generations
Dialogue: 0.0:33:56.16.0:33:59.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and that the Southern Air Temple was the first to fall.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:00.33.0:34:03.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..because you've been trapped in that ice this whole time.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:03.91.0:34:07.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The last time that the Great Comet was seen in the sky
Dialogue: 0.0:34:07.75.0:34:11.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..was 100 years ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:17.75.0:34:19.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He may seem like just a boy.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:19.75.0:34:21.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but he's much more.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:23.00.0:34:26.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He is the last Airbender.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:34.66.0:34:38.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Of all the places to drag our asses to. he picks the coldest spot in the world.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:38.29.0:34:41.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..How come his omens never take us somewhere with hot springs. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:46.54.0:34:48.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Something you wanna say. Lieutenant Jee?  - No. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:51.00.0:34:52.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Zuko:{\b0}{\c} Let me make something clear.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:52.83.0:34:56.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Our mission is vital to the future of the Fire Nation.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:56.79.0:34:59.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and so we will find the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:59.79.0:35:02.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We will prove ourselves worthy.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:02.04.0:35:04.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and we will see our homes and families again...
Dialogue: 0.0:35:08.08.0:35:09.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..or we will die trying.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:23.58.0:35:24.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:27.08.0:35:28.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..A hundred years.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:29.29.0:35:30.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..All my friends.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:31.04.0:35:32.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..everyone I know...
Dialogue: 0.0:35:34.87.0:35:36.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..they're all gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:37.29.0:35:38.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Um. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:40.62.0:35:43.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Believe me. I know how hard it is to lose the people you love.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:52.70.0:35:55.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..When I was little. I didn't really understand the war
Dialogue: 0.0:35:56.58.0:35:58.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..until the night the Firebenders came.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:00.87.0:36:02.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..They destroyed everything in their path.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:03.83.0:36:04.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Everything.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:06.20.0:36:07.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Everyone.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:10.45.0:36:12.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Afterwards. our father set out with the other warriors
Dialogue: 0.0:36:12.54.0:36:13.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..to hunt down the Firebenders.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:14.79.0:36:18.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..That was three years ago. and we haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:19.54.0:36:22.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He had left Sokka in charge when he just turned 13.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:23.58.0:36:25.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I guess he had to grow up fast.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:26.87.0:36:27.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We all did.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:30.66.0:36:33.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We're never really ready
Dialogue: 0.0:36:34.37.0:36:35.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..until we have to be.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:45.20.0:36:48.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..They were part of the Fire Nation's first attacks on the Water Tribe.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:49.33.0:36:50.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The Firebenders were ruthless.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:51.70.0:36:55.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Since then. the Fire Nation has conquered most of the world.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:56.54.0:36:58.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But the Waterbenders are still fighting back.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:59.29.0:37:00.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..especially in the North.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:00.45.0:37:02.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And the Earth Kingdom is still holding strong.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.25.0:37:05.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We hope.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:08.50.0:37:10.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I had friends in the Fire Nation.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:11.62.0:37:12.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I used to visit them.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:14.29.0:37:16.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..No one visits other nations now.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:17.16.0:37:18.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We're only friends with our own kind.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:31.62.0:37:34.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Good. Your skills have never been sharper.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:34.33.0:37:37.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I need to be at my best when I face the world's ultimate warrior.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:37.83.0:37:40.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..They say Avatar Kyoshi took down an entire squadron
Dialogue: 0.0:37:40.08.0:37:41.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..of Earth Kingdom soldiers single-handedly.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:41.91.0:37:44.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Well. you've certainly prepared enough.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:44.16.0:37:47.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Now. how about a nice cup of jasmine tea?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:51.12.0:37:54.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Say we find the Avatar. and you're able to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:54.70.0:37:58.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..a mission your father believed to be impossible.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:58.45.0:38:01.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And so your return home may be...
Dialogue: 0.0:38:02.91.0:38:03.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..unexpected.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:06.83.0:38:07.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:18.66.0:38:19.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Katara:{\b0}{\c} No one comes here.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:21.54.0:38:23.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's quiet and hidden.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:32.83.0:38:34.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're a Waterbender!
Dialogue: 0.0:38:35.50.0:38:38.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Barely. I'm trying to get better.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:38.00.0:38:40.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but I'm the only Waterbender left in the Southern Tribe.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:41.33.0:38:42.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka doesn't like it when I practice
Dialogue: 0.0:38:42.83.0:38:46.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..because he's worried that the Fire Nation will find out and...
Dialogue: 0.0:38:47.25.0:38:48.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And what?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:49.75.0:38:53.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..There's a reason I'm the only Waterbender left in the village.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:54.45.0:38:56.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..They've killed all the others.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:56.08.0:38:58.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka just doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:58.91.0:39:02.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm a warrior. I should be able to do more for our people.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:04.58.0:39:08.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The monks told me bending is about energy and balance.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:09.16.0:39:13.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..By feeling the energy around you. you can find balance.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:13.29.0:39:16.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..By finding balance. you can feel the energy.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:46.25.0:39:47.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Nice!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:47.79.0:39:49.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I wasn't even really trying.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:49.54.0:39:52.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..That's good. You just have to let go.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:58.45.0:39:59.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Katara?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:09.00.0:40:11.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka! Sokka. the Fire Nation. They're--
Dialogue: 0.0:40:11.41.0:40:13.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I know. We spotted them. Get to your posts now!
Dialogue: 0.0:40:15.66.0:40:17.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Sokka. the racks--  - Get them loaded.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:23.75.0:40:26.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't understand. Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:26.70.0:40:29.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..After all this time. what could they possibly want?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:29.95.0:40:31.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Him.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:32.04.0:40:35.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He's more than the last Airbender. Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:36.83.0:40:39.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You are the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:43.54.0:40:44.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:48.04.0:40:49.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I knew he was hiding something.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:50.12.0:40:54.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..When the world needed the Avatar the most. he vanished because he's a coward.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:54.08.0:40:56.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He ran. and people died.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:56.20.0:40:58.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka. they've landed.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:00.16.0:41:01.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You need to go hide.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:01.12.0:41:03.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Sokka. I wanna--  - Katara. now.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:07.00.0:41:08.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on. We need to get somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:26.45.0:41:27.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I am Prince Zuko.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:29.04.0:41:31.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Firstborn son of Fire Lord Ozai.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:31.87.0:41:33.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We have no desire to take your homes.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:34.54.0:41:37.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We merely seek someone who does not belong here.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:38.41.0:41:41.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Someone who is not one of you.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:42.29.0:41:43.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Turn him over now.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:44.75.0:41:46.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..or I'll burn this place to the ground.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:50.58.0:41:53.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Where is he?  - Sokka. you can't give him to them--
Dialogue: 0.0:41:53.08.0:41:55.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- He doesn't belong here.  - It's wrong. You know that!
Dialogue: 0.0:41:55.33.0:41:57.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..What I know is Dad told me to protect the village.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:57.33.0:41:59.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Yes. but remember what Mom told us too.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:00.45.0:42:03.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..She said that we have to protect those who can't protect themselves.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:03.08.0:42:05.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..He's lost everything he knows.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:05.66.0:42:08.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Sokka. don't you see? He's the Avatar!  - And he lied to us about it!
Dialogue: 0.0:42:09.70.0:42:12.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I know how hard this responsibility has been for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:13.08.0:42:15.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but there's more to being a leader than just catching fish.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:15.79.0:42:18.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You have to give people something to live for.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:18.87.0:42:20.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..That's what the Avatar is. He's hope.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:21.95.0:42:24.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And we need that just as much as we need food and shelter.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:25.91.0:42:26.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I know I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:57.79.0:42:58.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I am Sokka.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:59.83.0:43:00.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Son of Hakoda.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:00.95.0:43:01.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Lord of. uh.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:03.08.0:43:04.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Snow and Ice.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:04.95.0:43:07.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..On behalf of the Water Tribe Village of Wolf Cove.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:07.25.0:43:10.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I demand that you leave immediately!
Dialogue: 0.0:43:10.87.0:43:12.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..If this is the path you've chosen.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:13.58.0:43:14.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..then so be it.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:15.50.0:43:19.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Let's settle this between us! Leader to leader. You really need an army?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:20.00.0:43:22.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I thought you Firebenders had some guts.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:22.37.0:43:25.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Don't fall for it. We overpower them. It's no contest.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:25.75.0:43:27.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Well. where's the glory in that?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:30.41.0:43:31.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I accept.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:55.04.0:43:56.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Who needs an army now?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:09.04.0:44:10.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:22.87.0:44:23.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Can't be.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:39.20.0:44:40.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Ah!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:51.00.0:44:53.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Enough games. Burn the whole place to the ground.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:54.83.0:44:56.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..No!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:56.66.0:44:59.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'll go with you. Just leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:00.95.0:45:02.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm the one you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:05.83.0:45:07.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Get him.  - Wait!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:09.95.0:45:11.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} It's okay. Katara.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:12.79.0:45:14.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..No one has ever fought for me before.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:17.37.0:45:20.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I think you're the bravest person I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:53.04.0:45:56.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..We have to do something. Sokka. we have to help him. Sokka!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:56.45.0:45:57.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Okay. listen up.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:57.70.0:46:00.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Reinforce the braces on the gate. and don't fall behind on drills.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:00.66.0:46:03.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- I saw real sloppiness out there today.  - Drills?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:03.29.0:46:05.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And don't let the younger ones push you around.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:05.41.0:46:08.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You gotta let 'em know who's in charge. That's right.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:09.83.0:46:10.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're in charge.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:12.08.0:46:14.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Now. let's go save that weird kid.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:27.16.0:46:32.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..There are many who never imagined this day would ever come. myself included.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:33.62.0:46:35.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:36.08.0:46:37.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- Uh...  - Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:38.00.0:46:41.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm Iroh. son of Fire Lord Azulon.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:42.20.0:46:43.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And of course.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:44.83.0:46:47.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Why did the Fire Nation start this war?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:47.20.0:46:48.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Ah.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:49.33.0:46:51.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Some people say it is within our nature
Dialogue: 0.0:46:51.79.0:46:55.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..to expand and consume like fire itself.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:56.25.0:46:59.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Others believe that true stability in this world
Dialogue: 0.0:46:59.25.0:47:01.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..can only happen under our rule.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:01.87.0:47:05.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..so the drive to conquer is a drive for peace and unity.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:05.91.0:47:10.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..But peace comes from respecting life. not killing and destroying.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:10.25.0:47:12.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Iroh:{\b0}{\c} A noble sentiment. Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:12.12.0:47:14.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but in the end. for most of us.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:14.87.0:47:17.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..it doesn't matter how this war started.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:17.54.0:47:19.62.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It only matters how it can end.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:20.41.0:47:22.83.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..And the belief is that by capturing you.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:23.41.0:47:26.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..the Fire Nation can finally bring that about.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:27.58.0:47:29.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Is that what you believe?
Dialogue: 0.0:47:32.16.0:47:37.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I must leave. but I look forward to many more conversations with you. Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:38.16.0:47:42.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..In the meantime. I'll have some jasmine tea sent to you.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:42.00.0:47:44.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's quite soothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:15.08.0:48:16.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..- It won't be easy to catch them.  - I know.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:16.91.0:48:20.20.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Hopefully. we can find a swift current. Maybe draft off their wake.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:20.83.0:48:22.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Or
Dialogue: 0.0:48:23.16.0:48:24.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..we could go another way.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:25.95.0:48:27.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're not serious.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:28.29.0:48:32.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Katara. no! There's no way you're getting me on that...
Dialogue: 0.0:49:03.25.0:49:04.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} The Avatars.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:25.29.0:49:26.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Yes. sir. right away.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:45.08.0:49:46.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:49:47.62.0:49:48.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Zuko:{\b0}{\c} Stop him!
Dialogue: 0.0:49:49.70.0:49:51.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Get him!
Dialogue: 0.0:49:55.29.0:49:57.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Open fire. now!
Dialogue: 0.0:50:09.58.0:50:11.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Ah!
Dialogue: 0.0:50:36.25.0:50:37.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Hey. kid!
Dialogue: 0.0:50:37.91.0:50:39.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Sokka!
Dialogue: 0.0:50:46.25.0:50:47.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Ah!
Dialogue: 0.0:51:36.62.0:51:39.70.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} I can't believe you guys came for me. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:39.70.0:51:42.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's time we showed those flameheads they can't step on us.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:44.33.0:51:48.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The Firebenders aren't gonna give up. They're gonna keep coming after you.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:48.37.0:51:50.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Which means we can't go home.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:51.20.0:51:52.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It would put everyone in danger.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:56.83.0:51:58.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..So where do we go?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:23.45.0:53:24.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Gyatso.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:33.58.0:53:37.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Now. this would be a huge burden for anyone.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:37.58.0:53:39.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}but you're not just anyone. Aang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:53:40.87.0:53:42.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You're strong
Dialogue: 0.0:53:42.95.0:53:46.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..and kind and generous.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:47.12.0:53:48.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Remember that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:53:50.54.0:53:52.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Always remember who you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:54:05.33.0:54:06.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:11.83.0:54:14.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Sokka:{\b0}{\c} What's happening? What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:54:19.41.0:54:20.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Katara:{\b0}{\c} Aang!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:20.25.0:54:21.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Come on!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:30.50.0:54:31.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:37.20.0:54:39.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Katara:{\b0}{\c} Aang!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:39.25.0:54:40.54.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Stop this!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:44.37.0:54:45.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Please!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:50.87.0:54:51.95.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Aang!
Dialogue: 0.0:54:54.66.0:54:55.79.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Gyatso:{\b0}{\c} {\c&H38d832&\i1}Aang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:54:57.54.0:55:00.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I can't imagine a better person
Dialogue: 0.0:55:00.00.0:55:03.12.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..to have been given this power.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:07.70.0:55:09.16.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}You are my friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:55:11.08.0:55:13.66.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You will always be my friend.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:16.87.0:56:19.41.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Sokka:{\b0}{\c} So not to be rude. but what was that?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:20.16.0:56:21.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:22.62.0:56:24.33.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..There's so much I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:25.20.0:56:28.00.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..The monks are gone. and I'm all alone.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:29.37.0:56:30.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..You know.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:31.45.0:56:33.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..the thing about losing everything
Dialogue: 0.0:56:33.08.0:56:35.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..is that that's when you learn how strong you really are.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:36.75.0:56:38.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..It's when you learn to fight.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:41.16.0:56:44.04.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} They made the ultimate sacrifice for me.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:45.04.0:56:47.25.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I need to make sure their deaths weren't in vain.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:47.25.0:56:49.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I need to follow through on what they wanted me to do.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:49.45.0:56:52.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Complete my training and master all the other bending skills
Dialogue: 0.0:56:52.45.0:56:54.58.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..so I can bring balance back to the world.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:54.58.0:56:55.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..Oh. is that all?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:56.37.0:57:00.08.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..This was my home. and now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:03.25.0:57:04.91.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} {\c&H38d832&\i1}It's only after we've lost something{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:57:04.91.0:57:07.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}that we realize how much it means to us...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:57:12.62.0:57:14.87.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}and how we'd do anything to get it back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:57:18.41.0:57:19.37.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H3891e6&\b1}Aang:{\b0}{\c} {\c&H38d832&\i1}Anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:57:21.83.0:57:25.75.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I don't know where this will all lead. and I don't know if I have what it takes.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:26.83.0:57:28.50.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..but the one thing I do know is
Dialogue: 0.0:57:30.33.0:57:31.45.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..I'm the Avatar.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:32.12.0:57:34.29.Shadow No-Outline 720p..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}and this is just the beginning.{\i0}
